mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label: In Overwatch, the player can choose a hero from a rooster of 31 characters, like Soldier:76 in this diagram

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label:
Soldier:76 has a rifle and two abilities :

- Heal, who gives a total of 8% for ultimate
- Helix Rockets, who launch from rifle three rockets and gives 5% for ultimate
- Rifle, who gives 1 point for Body shot and 2% for Head shot

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label: To use Ultimate, the player needs to have 100% in the pool
